node.text:
Sharing my story has always been important to me - especially if it helps my refugee brothers and sisters share theirs. 
It was awesome to talk to fellow model and @refugees advocate @benstiller and share my journey from refugee camp to runway. We talked about a lot - from our common experiences on the runway for @maisonvalentino, our love for family, and the refugee crisis. 
Click the link in my bio to see how you can help! 
#EveryoneCounts #refugees #WithRefugees #RefugeeForum #UNHCR
